# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Pokemon TCG Restock Monitor — Environment Config
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env to Git.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Discord Webhook ────────────────────────────────
# Server Settings → Integrations → Webhooks → Copy URL
DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL=https://discord.com/api/webhooks/YOUR_WEBHOOK_ID/YOUR_WEBHOOK_TOKEN

# ── Email (Gmail) ──────────────────────────────────
# Use an App Password: myaccount.google.com → Security → 2-Step → App Passwords
EMAIL_FROM=youraddress@gmail.com
EMAIL_TO=youraddress@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx

# ── Twilio SMS ─────────────────────────────────────
# Get these from console.twilio.com
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=ACxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_auth_token_here
TWILIO_FROM_NUMBER=+15551234567
TWILIO_TO_NUMBER=+15559876543

# ── Monitor Settings ───────────────────────────────
CHECK_INTERVAL_MINS=5          # Check every N minutes (don't go below 3)
MAX_PRICE_THRESHOLD=0          # Global max price filter; 0 = use per-product max_price
